{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_34", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed there are no direct tests for `FinalAudioAssemblyService`, which is the cleanest place to add the missing assembly and publish failure coverage. I\u2019m checking the existing storage/test helpers now so the new suite uses the repo\u2019s normal primitives rather than bespoke shortcuts.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "timestamp": "2026-04-03T22:55:05.529406-07:00"}, "run_id": "852e59ae-7e3c-580a-9c17-7f38e0f42b62", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed there are no direct tests for `FinalAudioAssemblyService`, which is the cleanest place to add the missing assembly and publish failure coverage. I\u2019m checking the existing storage/test helpers now so the new suite uses the repo\u2019s normal primitives rather than bespoke shortcuts.", "timestamp": "2026-04-03T22:55:05.529406-07:00"}
