{"event_type": "planner.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"event_type": "codex.raw.agent_message", "event_version": "0.0", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_99", "text": "Implemented and verified the audio-pipeline test work. The code changes are checkpointed in commit `75d8511` (`feat(prompt-79): audio pipeline tests`).\n\nAdded a focused suite in [test_audio_pipeline.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_audio_pipeline.py), shared helpers in [audio_pipeline.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/support/audio_pipeline.py), a new segmentation regression in [test_narration_segmentation_service.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_narration_segmentation_service.py), and reviewer notes in [audio_pipeline_test_notes.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/audio_pipeline_test_notes.md). The required reviewer summary was written to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/79_audio_pipeline_tests/summary.md).\n\nVerification performed:\n- `cd backend && python -m ruff check --fix tests/test_audio_pipeline.py tests/test_narration_segmentation_service.py tests/support/audio_pipeline.py`\n- `cd backend && python -m ruff check tests/test_audio_pipeline.py tests/test_narration_segmentation_service.py tests/support/audio_pipeline.py`\n- `cd backend && python -m pytest tests/test_audio_pipeline.py tests/test_narration_segmentation_service.py` -> 7 passed\n- `cd backend && python -m pytest tests/test_audio_mixing_service.py tests/test_audio_music_service.py tests/test_gemini_tts_adapter.py` -> 9 passed\n- `cd backend && python -m pytest tests/test_story_tools.py -k \"audio\"` -> 7 passed, 34 deselected\n\nOne environment fix was needed during verification: `python-docx==1.2.0` was already declared in `backend/requirements.txt` but missing from the active environment, so I installed it. No browser checks were applicable because this task only changed backe